data.description: This is a large 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home with a lot of potential. Property was added onto for the potential of 2 master bedrooms with connected baths. The 2 car garage was also enclosed adding an extra 400 sq. ft. and could be a large den. The property was flooded at one time and the repairs were not finished. Property needs new septic system (see attached). This is a Fanniemae HomePath Property. Go to HomePath.com for more info.
